| Area | Before | After |
|---|---|---|
| **Security headers** | ❌ None | ✅ `helmet()` sets CSP, HSTS, X-Frame-Options, etc. |
| **Body parsing** | ❌ None | ✅ JSON + URL-encoded with 10kb size limit |
| **Rate limiting** | ❌ None | ✅ 100 req / 15 min per IP |
| **Input validation** | ❌ None | ✅ Query param type-checked (positive integer) |
| **Error handling** | ❌ Default Express (leaks stack) | ✅ Global handler, env-aware error messages |
| **404 handling** | ❌ Default HTML page | ✅ Consistent JSON `{ error }` response |
| **Port config** | ❌ Hardcoded `3000` | ✅ Configurable via `PORT` env var |

### Additional Recommendations (beyond this file)
